{"type": "article", "id": 8807, "title": "Kindle 白色版", "description": "", "date": "2015-04-23T07:16:56Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052351194l8IuUOPGJBDN5je.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t喜欢 Kindle 又觉得它的黑色外观沉闷无趣的人，有个好消息是，Kindle 最近推出了白色版本，且已经在中国发售了。同步预售的还有一系列五颜六色的保护套，以及 3 款来自漫画设计师陈安妮、寂地和大橘子的限量版保护套。白色版 Kindle 目前售价是 499 元人民币，而彩色保护套的售价是 49 元，限量版设计师保护套售价 89 元，<a href=\"http://www.amazon.cn/dp/B00KDRNYO4/ref=sa_menu_top_kindle_l1\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235116ewuUcmiWY1JdR6kV.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"1.05277778\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235116sYOxJv43NUBryjlp.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.82685185\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235117GV6npaJWwTHkrhgb.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.77867203\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235118CXkVO2fKTRU3w0jh.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.63796296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052351189bhxrAR4KlOF0fWn.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.4037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}